 My job was to bring something. I make a kick-ass chili. While I was talking to my step mom I was telling her the ingredients, two of the ingredients are beer and coffee (those two items although you cant taste them are essential to the recipe so I didn’t think it would good if I took them out). She said I couldn’t make it because of the beer and coffee I offered to put decafe coffee and the alcohol in the beer would burn off. She said it was the principle.<br>
<br>
Please enlighten me on why if there weren’t any alcohol and no caffeine this would be a problem. I don’t understand.<br>
<br>
